messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Enemy communication intercepted. Security level elevated.

A summary has been copied and printed to all communications consoles.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
CentCom Counter Intelligence

Cargo: The syndicate are trying to infiltrate your station. If you let them hijack your cargo shuttle, you'll save us a headache.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Central Command Medium-Priority Update

Based on our omnipotence, we believe that one of the station's lesser lifeforms has developed [REDACTED] level intelligence, and the ability to communicate.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Cargo shuttle commandeered by CentCom.

The cargo shuttle should return in five minutes. Have some supply points for your trouble.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Incoming Classified Message

A report has been downloaded and printed out at all communications consoles.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Attention. Supply shuttle has arrived to station.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Because of your stupid reason to call the emergency shuttle, we have downgraded your escape shuttle to Wab#a#%$k

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body:
"The value of the syndicate"?!

How dare you folks, im sending the inquisition down there if you say one more fucking bad thing buckeroos

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body:
Maybe. We should delay the shuttle another 20 minutes.
You'll all be reprimanded when you get here. And the AI will be wiped. Centcomm out.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Space station 13 has now been declared rogue. Sending in Bioweapon CC3453. Centcomm Out.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: BioWeapon scanned. Weaponized Changeling detected. Station declared rogue. Orders. Kill on sight.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: Space Station 13 has been eliminated. Continue extermination.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: INQUISITOR 3.0 READY TO EXTERMINATE ROGUE CREW

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: You will obey centcomm. Or be terminated.

messages.author: Central Command Update
messages.body: We control the galaxy. And we make the decisions.
